content: This looks amazing! I'd love to contribute to the backend.
Thanks! We'd love to have you on board. Check out our GitHub repo.
Great project! How are you handling the NLP part?
We're using GPT-4 API with custom fine-tuning for our use case.
Interested in the nutrition tracking feature. When will it be ready?
This is exactly what I need for my startup! Can I join?
Love the visualization features. What libraries are you using?
We're using D3.js for custom visualizations and Chart.js for standard charts.
How are you handling real-time messaging?
This component library looks professional. Great work!
Security is crucial for voting systems. Have you done a security audit?
Yes, we're working with security experts to audit the smart contracts.
IoT projects are fascinating! What sensors are you using?
This platform could revolutionize online education!
